================================================================================
ACADEMIC CITATION
================================================================================

When citing this project in academic work, please use:

  Monte Albán Heritage Center (MAHC). MAPSA: Monte Albán Primary Source
  Archive — Inscription Registry. Oaxaca, Mexico, 2026.
  https://registry.montealbanoaxaca.com

Individual records, interpretations, and photographs should be cited
according to the attribution and source metadata provided within each
record. Contributing scholars retain authorship credit for their
interpretive contributions.


